(1412, 146, 'details_0_detail_0_detail_text', 'Mike & Manny designed our ski camp to teach young racers how to ski better and faster. But what they really wanted to do was pass on the lessons they’ve learned on and off the slopes and share their passion for the sport. The Ski Camp gives young skiers from less fortunate financial situations the opportunity to succeed and move forward at pivotal points in their careers – when the costs and competitiveness of the sport begin to rise. \r\n\r\nMike & Manny designed our ski camp to teach young racers how to ski better and faster. But what they really wanted to do was pass on the lessons they’ve learned on and off the slopes and share their passion for the sport. The Ski Camp gives young skiers from less fortunate financial situations the opportunity to succeed and move forward at pivotal points in their careers – when the costs and competitiveness of the sport begin to rise. '),
