(2228, 192, 'our_team_2_team_member_0_bio', 'From Day one Nick has been the expertise as an actual ski coach for our Cowboys ski camps. Ski coaching as his profession, Nick has coached with the Canadian National World cup technical team, Whistler Mountain ski club, Fernie alpine racers and currently is the Men’s head coach of the BC Ski team. Raised in Kimberley and lives in Whistler, Nick is an integral part to creating a professional training environment for all the kids who attend our camp. '),
