(2600, 208, 'application_info_0_info_0_info_text', 'Mike & Manny Camp is open to 14 enthusiastic ski racers from across Canada who demonstrate, love and passion for ski racing first and foremost and secondly a strong consideration on low financial means for racing. Applicants must either be first year FIS (1998) or going into second year FIS next season (1997).'),
